===Glyph origin===
{{Han etym}}
Originally {{och-l|㝡}}, {{Han compound|ls=psc|宀|取|c1=s|c2=p|t1=roof|nocap=1}} – "to gather". Later {{och-l|*二}} was added as distinguishing marks to disambiguate the character for the meaning "the most". The top components have corrupted into {{och-l|*冃}} in the traditional form. These components were further corrupted into {{och-l|*曰}} in the simplified version.

